2. Inspect unofficial H2P's village role list: https://unofficialhowtoplay.co.uk/index.php/Village
3. Length of 3rd word denotes the row, length of 5th word denotes the column.
~~ Exception 1: Wolf-friendly factions ~~
Normally the 3rd word will have length from 1-9. It's length will be longer only if I get BMC/ Wulfkin Clan.
Length 10: BMC (https://unofficialhowtoplay.co.uk/index.php/Bloodmoon_Cult)
Length 11: Wulfkin Clan (https://unofficialhowtoplay.co.uk/index.php/Wulfkin_Clans)
Use length of 5th word to check the role.
~~ Exception 2: Other evil factions ~~
If the role is evil, my 2nd msg will be 1-4 words long. If the length of 1st word is:
1: Coven
2: Undead
3: Vamp
4: Demon
5: Neutral
6: Other
~~ Examples ~~
Example 1:
Hound 9:05: Nooooo
Hound 9:06: I can't believe they would kill my favorite lawyer Frank! Who could do such a thing?``
3rd word: Believe => Length 7 => Row 7
5th word: would => Length 5 => Column 5
Look at the chart on the UH2P. Column 5 (Mason Leader to Pagan). Row 7 (Novice Seer). So the check was novice seer.
Example 2:
Hound 9:03: We really should have lynched yesterday
Hound 9:03: Please, let's get him gone today.
3rd word: get => Length 3 => Row 3
5th word: gone => Length 4 => Col 4
Col 4 (Huntsman to Maple). Row 3 (Illuminati Lookout)
Example 3:
Hound 9:01: I still don't trust Wes' claim
Hound 9:01: It sounds fabricated, five days and you have no new intel?
3rd word: fabricated => Length 10 => BMC
5th word: days => Length 4
BMC (Blood Priest => Cultist). Row 4 (Cult Follower)
Example 4:
Hound 9:07: No deaths? Nice
Hound 9:09: brb, I have meta
Second message has <5 words => evil faction
1st word: Brb => Length 3 => Vamp
